The paper deals with color image analysis and pattern recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The study involves analyzing different image enhancement techniques, which can be related to machine learning (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as well. The paper also discusses the efficiency of different color spaces for segmentation, which can be related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
